Common.Strapline.Common.Text: BRAND NEW TILT PANEL WAREHOUSE IN TINGALPA

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:

The property is within 800m to the entrance of the Gateway Motorway providing excellent connectively to North and South, Port of Brisbane and Brisbane Airport.

Some of the main features of this opportunity are:

•	3,650sqm* of warehouse which can be split into two separate tenancies
•	200sqm* office accommodation split over two levels
•	Male and Female amenities plus kitchen
•	The warehouse offers min 7m internal clearance and accessed via two roller doors
•	Fully fenced and secured site with duel crossovers
•	Plenty of onsite car parking and hardstand for truck movement and container set down
•	Sub-leasing opportunity

For further information regarding this opportunity, please contact Exclusive Agents Ben Lyons of CBRE.
